  "text": "• EU Member States have undertaken binding national targets to increase the share of RES in their total energy consumption by 2020. [CITATION_1] Directive 2009/28 / EC provides that, by 2020 RES shall account for at least 20% of the total energy consumption in the EU. This Directive also provides that, by 2020 the use of renewable energy in transport (biofuel, electricity, and hydrogen produced from RES) amounts to at least 20% of the total fuel consumption in the EU.",
